dct_title_s: Map of Portage Routes and Old Trails in and Adjacent to Jay Cooke State Park, St. Louis County, Minnesota
dct_description_sm: Map of portage routes and trails in and around Jay Cooke State Park in St. Louis County, Minnesota. The map also includes the town of Cloquet, the St. Louis River and Fond Du Lac Park.
